      <p>I&#8217;ve made many a tomato sauce, but never, ever with butter&#8211;always olive oil. They&#8217;ve been good and some (after many hours of simmering) have been great, but never, ever spectacular. It must have been the lack of butter. Can&#8217;t wait to try this!</p>
