      <p>I just read your article, In Search of the perfect Meatball, in Bon Appetit. I can&#39;t wait to try (this weekend) your sauce and meatballs. Having an Italian mother-in-law, this will be a good comparison test.  Thanks for sharing the recipe in the magazine and your blog. I loved reading both stories.</p>
